description: Total Helium Ltd. operates as a helium exploration, production, and storage solutions company. It also engages in drilling operations at the Boltz 35B and the Miller 9D wells located in the Western Kansas. The company was formerly known as Wintertide Ventures Inc. and changed its name to Total Helium Ltd. in September 2021. Total Helium Ltd. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
